{"tid":1518210,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"與神同行 - 831 200萬人祈禱會","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T10:16:22.000Z","uid":55257,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf8e6bb40952edee8dc46bf6a0ed8bd163877d9","tid":1518210,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:29:54.000Z","msg":"與神同行 - 200萬人祈禱會<br />\n<br />\n代轉：我們是一群沒有連登account的60後基督徒，希望連登巴絲打支持我們舉辦這個「為香港罪人祈禱」大遊行，也歡迎不同宗教人士參與，例如歡迎市民帶同唸佛機出席遊行。<br />\n<br />\n召集十萬基督徒為香港罪人祈禱大遊行<br />\n<br />\n日期：31/8<br />\n時間：下午1230集合、1300起步(預計當日下午民陣會舉辦遊行，因此提早起步。)<br />\n集合地點：灣仔修頓球場<br />\n遊行路線：軒尼詩道&rarr;金鐘道&rarr;花園道&rarr;上亞厘畢道<br />\n活動詳情：遊行至循道衛理、警察總部、聖約翰座堂對開的花園道及禮賓府時，將稍作停留進行讀經和唱聖詩。<br />\n<br />\n註：由於是次活動為宗教活動，按公安條例可豁免向警方申請，是故將不會辦理不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n第一站：循道衛理香港堂<br />\n主題：為守護家園的香港人祈禱<br />\n<br />\n「非利士人也漸漸的迎著大衛來；拿盾牌的走在前頭。非利士人觀看、見了大衛、就藐視他；因為他年輕、面色光紅、容貌俊美。非利士人對大衛說、你拿杖到我這裡來、我豈是狗呢。非利士人就指著自己的神、咒詛大衛。」《撒母耳記上17:41-43》<br />\n<br />\n第二站：灣仔警察總部<br />\n主題：為將受懲罰的人祈禱<br />\n<br />\n「當下耶穌說：父阿、赦免他們；因為他們所作的、他們不曉得。」《路加福音23:34》<br />\n<br />\n第三站：聖約翰座堂<br />\n主題：為支持香港的列國祈禱<br />\n<br />\n「我憑公義興起古列、又要修直他一切道路；他必建造我的城、釋放我被擄的民、不是為工價、也不是為賞賜；這是萬軍之耶和華說的。」《以賽亞書45:13》<br />\n<br />\n終點站：禮賓府<br />\n主題：為罪人祈禱<br />\n<br />\n「這時候、賣耶穌的猶大、看見耶穌已經定了罪、就後悔、把那三十塊錢、拿回來給祭司長和長老說、我賣了無辜之人的血、是有罪了。他們說、那與我們有甚麼相干．你自己承當罷。猶大就把那銀錢丟在殿裡、出去屌死了。」《馬太福音27:3-5》<br />\n<br />\n（以上部份經文在遊行期間會以天主教聖經版本讀出）"},{"pid":"0ebf1f04653b95568458c19d51883616b0064fa0","tid":1518210,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUisWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=0886c5b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUisWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=6186901a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUisWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=96867ddf\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"fd7ebcf13dfdfb0056e02da5c26db62d9c37782f","tid":1518210,"uid":49575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6ROs2K.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6ROs2K.gif&h=de359aeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27d8f634521773587ca78f58df1f6791382cc0f2","tid":1518210,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"We are christian<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b3d15ff7fd5ceaf599e59df5995bc77c1ee952","tid":1518210,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"070149ddc24078e6bb04a1454d90131eaad91a51","tid":1518210,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41dbf404fba43b778c1f5440cb34f419f009330e","tid":1518210,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:34:57.000Z","msg":"831 同 818 一樣<br />\n要以人多、和理非取勝<br />\n加油 香港人!"},{"pid":"d7b0e7369037f99e063956e07b39cfdbbf8f6d9a","tid":1518210,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9f60e6546bcb834d314c98175b28dbc2473b3b","tid":1518210,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"b9c64e0756cf3c11617f0bb851e071c31292493b","tid":1518210,"uid":27804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cb01603174e6e93b598c988b48d4cfb64207fa","tid":1518210,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:37:49.000Z","msg":"有個問題 比人捉既時候可以比人質疑係咪信徒<br />\n建議大家即刻同d fd講自己信左耶蘇<br />\n第時都叫有證明自己係信徒"},{"pid":"620034b1fce9e021491567f30bf7a0cdcd4129e0","tid":1518210,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"行動Post 推返上頂呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見唔見哩家幾咁黑暗呀!? 黎明就到架喇!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂住呀 保持憤怒 never forgive, never forget<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c0e7b411c12d275eb25b5f3c0e7c95663671e3","tid":1518210,"uid":94502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"（正視聽）宗教遊行係要不反對通知書，只有宗教集會先唔駛<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1518225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1518225</a>"},{"pid":"6777e17eea38c549de82f23d70776763c687a8e2","tid":1518210,"uid":297272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"瑪竇福音25:45-46 <br />\n那時，君王回答他們說：我實在告訴你們：凡你們沒有給這些最小中的一個做的，便是沒有給我做。這些人要進入永罰，而那些義人卻要進入永生。"},{"pid":"5285f734fad7234c44d214eceeba8a4c109987b2","tid":1518210,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"呼籲基督徒去"},{"pid":"36d6a5df984e5f3268683d42360da2f748761b26","tid":1518210,